Sentencas: A simple method, without using lithography or etching processes, for fabricating a micro-solid oxide fuel cell (micro-SOFC) that utilizes a metal substrate is presented.
Titulo: Simple fabrication of micro-solid oxide fuel cell supported on metal substrate

Sentencas: A porous and thin (<25 mu m) metal (Ni) film is fabricated by screen printing a NiO film on a ceramic substrate and subsequently reducing this film.
Titulo: Simple fabrication of micro-solid oxide fuel cell supported on metal substrate

Sentencas: Electrolyte and the cathode layers are sequentially deposited on the Ni-film substrate.
Titulo: Simple fabrication of micro-solid oxide fuel cell supported on metal substrate

Sentencas: Micro-SOFCs with a thin-film Gd-doped ceria electrolyte, supported on the Ni substrate, are successfully tested at 450 degrees C. (C) 2008
Titulo: Simple fabrication of micro-solid oxide fuel cell supported on metal substrate
